He demanded states "undo" food aid already loaded on people's cards. Then he watched eight Senate Democrats cave to advance a shutdown deal with no guarantee on health care subsidies. Around midnight, he released pardons for 77 election conspiracists including four who pleaded guilty to crimes. We even learned Trump cut an unannounced deal with Hungary's Viktor Orban to protect that country's depressed currency. But Sunday's 60-40 vote was only procedural. item.title: X23 x Lady Deadpool Body Paint - MCroft07
item.description: I posted this on the internet and the internet got mad that I painted "wolverine wrong" and when I explained I was x23 they told me I should have found an audio that said "x23" instead of wolverine and then I gave up. Please be sentient in the comments, I have been on a blocking spree with some gross people I use body paint and do these in a mirror No, it is not AI I just looked at an anatomical drawing of a skeleton and copied it I use professional body paint covers (pasties) this means I am not wearing a top but I am also not naked. I paint myself, I make the props myself, I film myself, and I also edit. This is my full time thing now (yayy) I paint these by looking in a mirror, with brushes, and paint It takes between 6-12 hours each Body painting myself is my hobby/passion I do own clothes It doesn’t tickle “Why don’t you just wear clothes” once again, body painting myself is my hobby/passion. I am painting my skin, I am not wearing a suit - but that does not mean I am naked. I know, even I think this is a ridiculous set of questions I have to constantly answer I did not go to art school, I am self taught. Talent gets you so far, but this is a learned skill. The paint isn’t edible (gross) I've been painting myself for 16 years. The 07 does not mean I was born in 2007, UK 7 is my shoe size No, I don't need help painting my back, I don't want to paint my back, I don't need to paint my back. (also gross) No, I don't need help washing it off. (also you are gross) If you want to see more I am MCroft07 on IG, twitter, Tiktok, YouTube I paint them live on twitch I like doing the lip syncs, they're fun for me while I paint them. I couldn’t care less if you think they’re cringe. I am cringe but I am free My tattoos on my ribs are from Tomb Raider - I am a big TR fan I do not have an OF but if you want to send me money THAT badly you can just tip my twitch account. Haha. The shower afterwards takes about 15 minutes, I use a regular sponge and shower gel. The reason why it can look different at the end is because I am wearing a wig, I promise you it is not a different person because the hair changed. While on this topic, if my eyes change colour it’s because I am wearing contact lenses. (Those with an IQ above 10… I know. Even I’m shocked the wig thing is a frequent comment). I use body paint. It doesn’t tickle, I am very ticklish and this is fine. I don’t have an allergic reaction to the paint, but if you do it, you should always do a patch test first I do not know where you can buy body paint in every country. I know in the UK it is available at FacePaintingshop.com. I use a plethora of different brands, it’s best to search for them yourself online. I don’t work in Hollywood, I don’t want to. I just want to improve my body painting for myself. I am English, not American. I do not go outside like this to scare people. 1, that would be very cold. 2, in this current age, everyone would take photos without me knowing and it would likely dox me :)))))) I’m not a sweaty person, but if I was this would be a lot more difficult. Thank you to those of you who came from Imgur to my Twitch channel! “What’s the point in painting yourself when you can wear clothes?” all my clothes are in the laundry, had to resort to this, tough life It would not be quicker to jump into a pool of paint - think of the drying time?! If you're still here I'm procrastinating cleaning my wig wardrobe by posting this I don’t care that I wash it off at the end, I get to reuse this canvas, we love a reduce, reuse, recycle queen. I am not the lady who did the Maneskin video, it’s a cool video and she slayed, but it isn’t me. I can promise you there is not *a man* painting these and I am pretending to paint myself. I am genuinely painting myself. I know a lot of you don’t like reading this faq because it is horrid to see that I have to answer all of these. Unfortunately I have noticed that when I don’t put in all the icky things then I get more gross comments and I just have to spend more time blocking people so it’s better to call it out. I just copy and paste it each time anyway.

item.title: I'm going to die soon
item.description: Life's unfair and the faster you accept it the easier it is to live. But today life really sucks, the last hope was taken away from me, the cancer mutated and there's no hope for a cure. Two years of chemo, radiation, immunotherapy therapy, a stemcell transplantation, the cancer coming back, sepsis, severe pneumonia, pneumothorax, severe anemia and more days in hospital than at home. I'm only thirty and I don't wanna leave my friends, family and my soulmate. It hurts every time I have to tell them bad news and this is the worst. I've talked to a photographer so they'll have a picture for my funeral. My cancer is aggressive and the doctor's tell me untreated I'll be dead in a few months. Hug the people you love and appreciate them ❤️

item.title: Senator Schumer should step down as Minority Leader of the United States Senate. Please contact these key leaders of the United States Senate Democratic Caucus expressing your concern about Chuck Schumer and why he should resign from this position.
item.description:
Amy Klobuchar Chair of the Steering & Policy Committee for the Senate Democrats 202-224-3244 klobuchar.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/email-amy
Mark Warner Vice‑Chair of the Senate Democratic Caucus 202-224-2023 warner.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/contact
Brian Schatz Deputy Democratic Conference Secretary in the Senate 202-224-3934 schatz.senate.gov/contact/share-your-thoughts
Your own U.S. Senator . Your local Senator represents you directly and may be more responsive to constituent pressure than those further up the leadership chain. U.S. Senate switchboard is (202) 224-3121 senate.gov/senators/senators-contact
"I’m calling today because I’m deeply concerned about the direction of our party’s leadership in the Senate. In particular, I believe that Senator Schumer should step down from his position as Leader of the Senate Democrats so that fresh leadership can better respond to the challenges ahead. As a member of the Senate Democratic Caucus and you have the influence to help initiate this change. In doing so, you would unite the caucus and restore trust. Continued leadership under Senator Schumer is no longer serving the best interests of the caucus or our party’s ability to move boldly. A new Leader would signal renewal and a recommitment to effective, responsive leadership."
Senator Schumer, I am writing to you as a concerned citizen deeply invested in the future of our Democratic Party and the country. Recent events and decisions have led me to believe that your continued leadership as Senate Democratic Leader is no longer serving the best interests of the caucus or the American people. Your recent choices, particularly in the handling of the government shutdown have raised serious concerns about your ability to effectively unite and guide the caucus during these politically dangerous times. For the sake of restoring faith in Senate leadership and ensuring the Democratic Party can move forward with strength, and unity, I respectfully urge you to consider stepping down from your leadership position. Doing so would give a renewed direction at a time when strong, principled leadership is desperately needed. I hope you will act in the best interest of the party and the American people.
